The 12 individual spreadsheets used for this project can be found at the data link in the Google Data Analytics course capstone project (see pdf in this file) which is pasted again below. 
The months used were July 2025 to June 2026. GitHub signalled that the spreadsheets were too big to upload directly but anyone interested should be able to find them online this way. 

